5c35ff9526eb5a239e384025d20840ef159ad1f82922a49bb92ebd251c61410361495da9b03a5e185a26c6ad587ece68a20bd7973cad05cbb4f6cd490a4cbf37  0001-fbdev-support-RGB32-framebuffer-with-BGR-order.patch"
